item.title: By: Tisha F.
item.dc:creator: Tisha F.
item.description:
Love the NKOTB reference. Of course I was a total fan and of course my favorite with poor Jonathan. LOL! He's just feminine enough for me. And my second: Joey!
Oh yeah! Why I am commenting. Having got the "luscious lips" like you, this is a staple in my going out regimen. Now I have song to go along with it! Hang Tough!
